{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm-- I was-- I don't-- I was 14-year-old, but I was small and-- and quite thin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so how I got it into the camp was just by the good luck of Mengele had-- had a whim.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was worried about the future.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother could have-- could have been gone away, but he always-- to-- from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to stay in Auschwitz because those-- those chimneys were constantly burning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I knew what's going on a few hundred yards from us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but I was never taken into-- away into-- into transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when it came to selection, it started in the autumn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Immediately, the first selection, which was Erev Rosh Hashanah, the day before Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I was selected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at that time, they were not very strict on the selection because they told the children that-- that the children are being selected to be taken to a children camp who are getting much better conditions.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] But most of the children there were naive, so we'll just-- they didn't need much encouragement to go the children camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I didn't want to go to the children camp because I-- I knew what-- I had a-- I knew what it mean, children camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was not difficult to-- getting-- getting out of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What people-- what people told me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had an instinct that-- that this is-- that this is-- the Germans are not making for the children a special treatment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they take children, it's because they are useless for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Possibly, because-- because-- a lot of-- a lot of people even older than me, and they just went like the sheep to-- to-- to the selections.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
